Package entity

Class Project

Object
Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Project extends Object implements Serializable
A project with various attributes, including information about units, applications, bookings, and more. This class provides methods for managing and interacting with project data.

      units - A list of units in the project.
      applicationOpenDate - The date the application opens.
      applicationClosingDate - The date the application closes.
      visibility - The visibility status of the project.
      officerSlots - The number of officer slots available.
